==Definition== '''‘Pokies’''' – Pronounced- '''po•kies''' and '''po•keys''' 
'''''Noun''''' ''(sometimes used in singular, pokie machine)'' - A Poker Machine or [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poker_machine Slot Machine]
===Origin=== – Comes from [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Australian_English Australian Slang,] an evolution of the Australian vernacular, ''“I’m off to play the Poker Machines down at the [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RSL RSL]”'' became, ''“I’m off to play the Pokies down at the [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RSL RSL]”'' Thought to have originated in [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_South_Wales New South Wales] in the 1970’s.

